    "translation": "过度使用可能导致疾病",
    "stage": 5,
    "context": "text = 'Overindulgence may lead to sickness'"
  },
  {
    "ID": 293417433,
    "key": "Right-click or drag onto the currently selected character in order to eat. This item will be consumed in the process.",
